"uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"我想知道話唔想有二處損害嗰個，如果嗰條友放返出嚟再強姦返佢老母或者佢個女個會有咩諗法。<br />\n<br />\n法庭就係俾人判到底有冇罪，並唔係一個感情嘅地方。"},{"pid":"799ad01201296f636720415b8db5469eda984899","tid":486439,"uid":761,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"女權臭閪"},{"pid":"d52967a7601be96b190d4d207bd16320f85c1010","tid":486439,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:43:06.000Z","msg":"香港算唔算係女權最成功嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0187eda4b485eb8cf58d9d49100475d3bc1c007","tid":486439,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"好撚煩"}]}